# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# time4transfer — local environment template
# Copy to .env.local and fill in real values. Never commit .env.local.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Google Places API (New) — pickup / drop-off autocomplete.
# Required for production-quality address search.
# When unset, the app falls back to OpenStreetMap Nominatim (free, lower quality).
#
# How to obtain:
#   1. https://console.cloud.google.com → create a project
#   2. Enable the "Places API (New)" for that project
#   3. Credentials → "Create credentials" → API key
#   4. Restrict the key to the Places API only; restrict by HTTP referrer in prod
#   5. Paste the key below and restart `npm run dev`
GOOGLE_PLACES_API_KEY=YOUR_API_KEY_HERE
